<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2>Reset your password, <%= name %></h2>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your AuthSphere account. Click the button below to set a new password:</p>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= url %>" style="background-color: #E53E3E; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">Reset Password</a>
    </p>
    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= url %>"><%= url %></a></p>
    <p>This link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.</p>
</body>
</html>
